<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="38_Canadian_Brigade_Group">38 Canadian Brigade Group</span></h4>
<p><a href="/wiki/38_Canadian_Brigade_Group" title="38 Canadian Brigade Group">38 Canadian Brigade Group</a> (38 CBG) is a <a href="/wiki/Primary_Reserve" title="Primary Reserve">Reserve Force</a> brigade group based out of <a href="/wiki/Winnipeg,_Manitoba" title="Winnipeg, Manitoba" class="mw-redirect">Winnipeg, Manitoba</a>. It's composed of units in <a href="/wiki/Saskatchewan" title="Saskatchewan">Saskatchewan</a>, <a href="/wiki/Manitoba" title="Manitoba">Manitoba</a> and eastwards into <a href="/wiki/Ontario" title="Ontario">Ontario</a> to <a href="/wiki/Thunder_Bay,_Ontario" title="Thunder Bay, Ontario" class="mw-redirect">Thunder Bay, Ontario</a>.</p>
