<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="39_Canadian_Brigade_Group">39 Canadian Brigade Group</span></h4>
<p><a href="/wiki/39_Canadian_Brigade_Group" title="39 Canadian Brigade Group">39 Canadian Brigade Group</a> (39 CBG) is a <a href="/wiki/Primary_Reserve" title="Primary Reserve">Primary Reserve</a> brigade group based out of <a href="/wiki/Vancouver,_BC" title="Vancouver, BC" class="mw-redirect">Vancouver, BC</a>. All of the units of the brigade are from the province of <a href="/wiki/British_Columbia" title="British Columbia">British Columbia</a>.</p>
