<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="41_Canadian_Brigade_Group">41 Canadian Brigade Group</span></h4>
<p><a href="/wiki/41_Canadian_Brigade_Group" title="41 Canadian Brigade Group">41 Canadian Brigade Group</a> (41 CBG) is a <a href="/wiki/Primary_Reserve" title="Primary Reserve">Reserve Force</a> brigade group based out of <a href="/wiki/Calgary,_Alberta" title="Calgary, Alberta" class="mw-redirect">Calgary, Alberta</a>. The units forming the brigade group are from the province of <a href="/wiki/Alberta" title="Alberta">Alberta</a>, as well as a company based out of <a href="/wiki/Yellowknife" title="Yellowknife">Yellowknife, Northwest Territories</a>.</p>
